item.title: Golf Cart Tour - South Tama Rec Trail
item.description: Ever been interested in discovering the South Tama Rec Trail and learning more about the trail and future plans? Well, on Wednesday, May 25, we will sponsor a golf cart tour of the South Tama Rec Trail. Individuals and families may join us between Noon and 3pm at either the Tama Civic Center or Toledo Heights Park for a golf cart ride on the trail. Some of our planning material is available below.
